('wk1_19', 'ccc_27', 'ccc_14', 1, '2017-09-08', '19:00:00', 'Hall High School', 1, 0, 7, 0, 0, NULL, 14, 14, 0, 14, NULL, 'ccc_27', NULL, 'Rafael Nieves carried Simsbury with four touchdowns to a 42-7 win over Hall in a CCC West game at Hall High School Stadium. \r\nNieves scored on runs of 97, 12 and 55 yards throughout the game with Tate Valerio catching a 10 yard pass from Jackson Masters. Angel Serrano scored in the second quarter on a 4 yard run and Kory Zall made every kick for Simsbury''s extra points.\r\nDesmond Richards scored for Hall on a 4 yard run. ', 'First Quarter\r\nS—Rafael Nieves run (Kory Zall kick)\r\nS—Tate Valerio 10 pass from Jackson Masters (Zall kick)\r\nSecond Quarter\r\nH—Desmond Richards 6 run (Sam Harrington kick)\r\nS—Nieves 97 run (Zall kick)\r\nS—Angel Serrano 4 run (Zall kick)\r\nFourth Quarter\r\nS—Nieves 12 run (Zall kick) \r\nS—Nieves 55 run (Zall kick)', 'S', 'H', 42, 7, NULL),
