('wk1_57', 'ccc_04', 'ccc_15', 1, '2017-09-09', '13:00:00', 'Hartford Public High School', 1, 6, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 14, 6, 6, NULL, 'ccc_04', 'Hickey''s Feet Boost Bristol Central', 'Quarterback Dathan Hickey ran for three touchdowns to lead Bristol Central to a 26-6 win over Hartford Public Saturday in a CCC Div. II game at Hartford Public High School.\r\n\r\nHickey was the game''s leading rusher with 22 carries for 163 yards, scoring on runs of 4, 3 and 2 yards. He was 7-for-11 through the air for 86 yards. Darrell Payton also contributed a 9-yard TD run for Bristol (1-0), and finished with 11 rushes for 56 yards.\r\n\r\nLavarey Banton had a 4-yard TD run to give Hartford Public (0-1) a 6-0 lead in the first quarter, and finished with 24 rushes for 118 yards. He also had 16 tackles on defense.', 'First Quarter\r\nHP--Lavarey Banton 4 run (kick failed)\r\nSecond Quarter\r\nBC--Dathan Hickey 4 run (kick failed)\r\nBC--Hickey 3 run (Hickey run)\r\nThird Quarter\r\nBC--Darrell Payton 9 run (kick failed)\r\nFourth Quarter\r\nBC--Hickey 2 run (pass failed)', 'BC', 'HP', 26, 6, NULL),
('wk1_58', 'ccc_30', 'ccc_24', 1, '2017-09-09', '13:00:00', 'RHAM High School', 1, 6, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 10, 0, NULL, 'ccc_30', 'Late Interception Seals Win For Tolland', 'Jon Glick stopped a last-minute RHAM drive with an interception in the end zone to secure a 10-6 win for Tolland in a CCC Div. III East game Saturday at RHAM High School in Hebron.\r\n\r\nGlick nabbed the interception for Tolland with 27 seconds remaining in the fourth quarter, halting a 60-yard drive by RHAM. After falling behind 6-0 early, Tolland took a 7-6 lead on Ryan Carlson''s 6-yard touchdown run. Jonny Lindquist followed with a 27-yard field goal to extend the lead.\r\n\r\nCarlson finished with 56 rushing yards and passed for 106. Lindquist was the leading receiver with 5 catches for 76 yards, and Collin Cook had 46 rushing yards for Tolland.', 'First Quarter\r\nR--#8 1 run (kick failed)\r\nThird Quarter\r\nT--Ryan Carlson 6 run (Jonny Lindquist kick)\r\nT--Lindquist 27 FG', 'T', 'R', 10, 6, NULL),
