('wk2_62', 'pqt_09', 'pqt_02', 2, '2017-09-16', '13:00:00', 'Coginchaug High School', 1, 14, 6, 6, 8, NULL, 6, 14, 0, 6, NULL, 'pqt_02', NULL, 'Coginchaug''s Pat Ladas rushed for 110 yards on 18 carries with one touchdown resulting in a 34-26 Coginchaug victory over Haddam-Killingsworth at Coginchaug High School in Shoreline Conference play.\r\nEli Rivera added to the score throwing 7, 90 and 29 yard touchdown passes and running for another. Though tied at half time, Ladas and Rivera continued to press running for another touchdown each in the second half.\r\nTobey Callender led for H-K with 95 yards on 15 carries and one touchdown. \r\nKevin Dougherty ran for two touchdowns with Zach Kaufmann catching a 29 yard pass for a touchdown.', 'First quarter\r\nHK-Kevin Dougherty 3 run (kick failed)\r\nC-Kevin Cross 7 pass from Eli Rivera (Ryan Cross kick)\r\nC-Anthony Curry 90 pass from Rivera (Cross kick)\r\nSecond quarter\r\nC-Curry 29 pass from Rivera (kick failed)\r\nHK-Zach Kaufmann 29 pass from Cody Ellex (Tobey Callender run)\r\nHK-Callender 7 run (run failed)\r\nThird quarter\r\nC-Pat Ladas 7 run (kick failed)\r\nFourth quarter\r\nHK-Dougherty 1 run (pass failed)\r\nC-Rivera 3 run (Ladas run)', 'HK', 'C', 26, 34, NULL),
